text: The Australian Labor Party (New South Wales Branch), commonly known as NSW Labor, is the New South Wales branch of the Australian Labor Party, a centre- left social democratic political party in Australia. It is currently in Government (having formed a minority government since 2023). The party's leader is Chris Minns (who is the current state Premier) and the party's deputy leader is Prue Car.
